&lt;p&gt;PyCon Canada happened in November, in Montreal. It was freezing cold outside, but didn&amp;rsquo;t stop me from getting ice cream.
I found La Cabane De Danny, and they make ice cream with bubble waffle cone. So fun! The matcha ice cream was real good!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Unfortunately this shop has since closed down.&lt;/p&gt;
